85. List the steps to get file name from a path in PHP.
code:
<?php
$path = "/var/www/html/sample.txt";

// Method 1: Using basename()
$filename1 = basename($path);
echo "File name using basename(): $filename1<br>";

// Method 1b: Remove extension using basename()
$filename2 = basename($path, ".txt");
echo "File name without extension using basename(): $filename2<br>";

// Method 2: Using pathinfo()
$filename3 = pathinfo($path, PATHINFO_BASENAME);
echo "File name using pathinfo(): $filename3<br>";

// Method 2b: Using pathinfo() to get filename without extension
$filename4 = pathinfo($path, PATHINFO_FILENAME);
echo "File name without extension using pathinfo(): $filename4<br>";
?>

